The paper focuses on object proposal approaches using convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for reranking proposals. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) as the primary sub-category. The use of CNNs also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of data-driven approaches, which could fall under neural networks (cs.NE) or information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
